增加路由规则，将网卡eth1  80端口的请求转发到8000端口:
    iptables -A PREROUTING -t nat -i eth1 -p tcp --dport 80 -j REDIRECT --to-port 8000
    cd /etc/rc.d/init.d
    ./iptables save

